&lt;p>References&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote></description></item><item><title>mstsc.exe端口修改</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/mstsc.exe%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9/</link><pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 08:36:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/mstsc.exe%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
&lt;p>💡 mstsc 是 Microsoft Terminal Services Client 的缩写，是用于远程桌面连接的工具。通过它，你可以使用 Windows 自带的远程桌面协议（RDP）连接到其他 Windows 设备的桌面环境。通过 Win + R，然后输入 mstsc，打开远程桌面连接界面。&lt;/p>&lt;/blockquote>
&lt;hr>
&lt;ol>
&lt;li>打开注册表&lt;/li>
&lt;li>修改端口号
HKEY_LOCAL_MACHINE\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\Terminal Server\WinStations\RDP-Tcp PortNumber 为 xxxx&lt;/li>
&lt;li>防火墙设置&lt;/li>
&lt;li>启动服务&lt;/li>
&lt;li>勾选设置&lt;/li>
&lt;li>重启电脑&lt;/li>
&lt;/ol></description></item><item><title>CMD Common commands</title><link>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/cmd-common-commands/</link><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 01:52:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://Pan-Binghong.github.io/daily-learning/devops/cmd-common-commands/</guid><description>&lt;blockquote>
